Package: BRcal
Title: Boldness-Recalibration of Binary Events
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Adeline P.", "Guthrie", , "apguthrie47@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID")),
      person("Christopher T.", "Franck", , "chfranck@vt.edu", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID")))
Description: This package facilitates boldness-recalibration at a user specified 
             level of calibration via the `brcal()` function. Supporting functions 
             to assess calibration via Bayesian and Frequentists approaches, 
             MLE recalibration, LLO-adjust via any specified
             parameters, and visualize results are also provided.   
             See Guthrie & Franck (2024) for methodological details.
